{"tid":1830818,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特斯拉落戶歐洲邁進一步 3.5億購德國工業地","createTime":"2020-01-20T02:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T10:51:18.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2b8c8b92f510e3e79f855ae4efe9b439073ab00c","tid":1830818,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T02:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/20/101648_0584bb816efb399fb5a50000fc07135f.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F20%2F101648_0584bb816efb399fb5a50000fc07135f.jpeg&h=084d6692&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n德國布蘭登堡 (Brandenburg)邦政府發言人證實，美國電動車特斯拉(Tesla)已同意購入邦內的一幅土地。此舉意味特斯拉很可能快將落實在德國設立首間歐洲工廠的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n特斯拉去年11月公布有意在德國建立超級工廠，以便爭取歐洲市場。<br />\n<br />\n布蘭登堡邦發言人Florian Engels指，特斯拉將購入一幅位於格林海德市附斤的300公頃工業用地，作價為4091萬歐羅(3.53億港元)，邦議會財政委員會已經於1月9日批准有關出售交易。特斯拉發言人證實有關消息。<br />\n<br />\n當地政客、工會與工業團體歡迎特斯拉的舉動。不過，有250名居民則發動示威，反對有關交易，指特斯拉設廠可能影響當地生態。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2357682/all\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2357682%2Fall&d=3W3ENIgnTPsh0%2B1doSs%2BP2iIh%2BLW8fuN5Q3LPFa5L7A%3D&h=f93c545a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2357682/all</a>"},{"pid":"a681da4e71aef0e546d831ce109aa337cacecc7c","tid":1830818,"uid":47239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T02:37:13.000Z","msg":"TSLA<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd6a0a37a681d161d3afbb0f1c9246f9891ab56","tid":1830818,"uid":308567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T02:41:15.000Z","msg":"劍指700蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e516c07b4dd85c2239a41727c4ed5e01a8eb0499","tid":1830818,"uid":129309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cd6a0a37a681d161d3afbb0f1c9246f9891ab56","tid":183